songs.title: E.T.
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: All]
You’re an alien

[Verse 1: Jade & All]
You’re so hypnotising
Could you be the devil, could you be an angel?
Different DNA
They don’t understand you

[Pre-Chorus: Perrie & All]
You’re from a whole another world
A different dimension
You open my eyes
And I'm ready to go lead me into the light

[Chorus: All & Perrie]
Kiss me, k-k-kiss me
Infect me with your loving, fill me with your poison
Take me, t-t-take me
Wanna be a victim, ready for abduction
Boy, you’re an alien
You’re touch so foreign
It’s supernatural
Extra-terrestrial

[Bridge: All]
They say be afraid, they say be afraid
They say be afraid, they say be afraid

[Pre-Chorus: Perrie & All]
You’re from a whole another world
A different dimension
You open my eyes
And I'm ready to go lead me into the light

[Chorus: All]
Kiss me, k-k-kiss me
Infect me with your loving, fill me with your poison
Take me, t-t-take me
Wanna be a victim, ready for abduction
Boy, you’re an alien
You’re touch so foreign
It’s supernatural
Extra-terrestrial
